      <h2 class="block-title">About MEPC</h2>
    

      
            <div class="field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field--item"><p>The Middle East Policy Council is a nonprofit organization whose mission is to contribute to American understanding of the political, economic and cultural issues that affect U.S. interests in the Middle East.</p>

